HTC Says Microsoft Hasn’t Increased Handset Royalty Fees

-- B y   A d e l a   L i n
-- 
2011-05-30T01:40:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/htc-says-microsoft-hasn-t-increased-handset-royalty-fees.html
HTC Corp. (2498)  said  Microsoft Corp. (MSFT)  hasn’t
raised royalty fees for using Android operating systems in its
handsets, the Taiwanese company said in a statement to the stock
exchange today. The reports by Taipei-based Economic Daily News
and Commercial Times today the U.S. company will raise charges
aren’t true, it said  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adela Lin in Taipei at 
 alin95@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Janet Ong at 
 jong3@bloomberg.net  